data.description: Located in a peaceful and established neighborhood in Illini Bluffs school district, this ranch style home has everything you need to make it your own private oasis. Upon entering you will see a large living room with nice sized picture window. The kitchen boasts potential with its functional layout, and with some TLC, it can easily be transformed into a chef's dream space. All appliances AS-IS. The three bedrooms upstairs offer ample room for your family or guests.  The primary bedroom features an en-suite bathroom for added privacy. Downstairs you will find a sprawling, unfinished walk-out basement just waiting for your personal touch! Possible 4th bedroom just needs the finishing touches. One of the standout features of this property is the amazing garage, providing ample space for your vehicles, storage, or even a workshop. The accompanying shed adds even more storage options, perfect for those with hobbies or a green thumb. The corner acre lot allows for endless possibilities - expand the garden, install a pool, or create your own outdoor oasis. The potential is limited only by your imagination!! New Roof and Gutters- 2023, Water Heater- 2021
